Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.54,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.45,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.26,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:22.75,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:27.48,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:34.42,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, great! Your bed is softer than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lights out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I didn't call.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, dear Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...it all began that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...when Mariko-san suddenly showed up at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, I hadn't the slightest idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...what sort of pain she was feeling, or why.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,27. An Incident of Bloodshed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I came over so suddenly last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father and mother are so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after barging in like that, they said, "come and visit us again"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when can I visit again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Tomoko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san! Since when do you catch the train here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Curious, aren't you? Well, I stayed at Nanako-san's last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to take Nanako away from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No time for any more practice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sweaty! That's a drawback of morning practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and there's never enough time for a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really improved a lot, Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See you at lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san, your slippers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Ishikawa. I'm not in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave your name and a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see your notes. I didn't understand that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but I might not have it right, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,1st period French...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, that's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose even a Sorority member can forget her homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority represents the student body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So perhaps you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...should get your lives under better control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to then, Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if you tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...some things in your life just can't be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so, Shinobu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, if you have something to say, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is there really something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reaction tells me I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san, class is starting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"A pornographer's legacy is pornography."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So what lies in store for the daughter of a pornographer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bitches like you never know when to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, Kaoru-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate her, I hate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That really hurt. You're more vicious than my dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a low-down filthy bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bark as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be at Seiran for that much longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san has to leave Seiran?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, our generation prefers tight jeans over cotton pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...since we have confidence in our figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko, you nut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what. My parents are getting divorced!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Divorced?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look so serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't bother me one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A man finds a lover, has an affair, then leaves his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so common these days that it doesn't even make good TV drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See! Didn't I always tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...men just can't be trusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's such a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My home is so dreary now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping for lots of alimony!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother... Divorce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san's parents are going to divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san spoke about it so lightly in front of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But this must've been the reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...the reason that she cried so sadly at my house last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, that same Mariko-san is cheerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...but her cheerfulness is forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do, my dear Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for her, as her friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... It'll just be a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like... to see you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is sort of... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mariko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... is she done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you come along with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's so soft! Puyo puyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Tomoko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yes! You're right! See, Nanako! Feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:11:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks great on you, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a bit too subdued?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's very chic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the bill to the usual address.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really spend that much without asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's accessorize it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Accessories, 4th floor please."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my thanks for coming shopping with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, chocolate cake and lemon tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all? Don't hold back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that hungry, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll have Key-lime pie, sorbet, crepes suzettes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then lemon tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang! You're too extravagant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's what you always say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never change, I guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So... this is why... this is why you wouldn't see me today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.21,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko? Is that you, Mariko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Mariko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come home last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san's mother called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was so lonely without you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry. Dinner will be ready soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I made your favorite, beef stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Papa today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman was with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you can say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you pretend it's nothing all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you say anything? Why don't you get angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You care about him don't you? You love him don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You cry because he's gone don't you? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Mariko! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama you're crying again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! You forgot this. We brought it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally decided to just spend a lot of time with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The pending divorce was a major problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I was powerless over something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...but staying close to her might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to help Mariko-san directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I hoped to ease her pain at least a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured that would be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But, my Dear Brother, I was too optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That afternoon, my optimistic plans were destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shinobu-san! I didn't think you'd show up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You have such a famous father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shinobu's divorce is official.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, big headlines, and a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father's lover used to be an actress...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're met her, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know all about it don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It says how much alimony your mother's getting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not one of the all-knowing members of the Sorority like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you can take this... take a look at it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's the end for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your family gives a big endowment to Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Without it you may lose your membership in the Sorority,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...and your attendance at Seiran itself could be at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But knowing you, you might still choose your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a difficult decision: take the money, or dump your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mu... Mu... Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Shinobu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Mariko-san's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it was really her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:15.00,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.00,0:24:20.47,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:26.08,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.08,0:24:31.55,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.29,0:24:37.83,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.83,0:24:43.30,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.30,0:24:46.03,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.03,0:24:48.84,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.84,0:24:51.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.24,0:24:56.51,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.22,0:25:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When she learns that the divorce caused this incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.65,0:25:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko's Mother is ridden with guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.50,0:25:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko is also overcome with guilt feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.25,0:25:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Their family's love leads to their family's destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.07,0:25:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: The Christmas Candles
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.65,0:25:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
